Four files are in this repository.

Datasheet-samplesizes.csv includes all data and has to be downloaded along with the R code in order for it to work.

Sample sizes - R-Code.R is the R-Code used for this paper. It is annotated with comments for better readability.

spreadsheet manual.docx provides the guidelines used when coding studies in detail.

1-s2.0-S1469029215300273-mmc1.docx explains how the power analyses in G*Power were conducted. This is the same file as the one Schweizer & Furley (2016) used.